SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT ACCC_CHANGENO, ACCC_DATVALUE, ACCC_MUTTYPE, ACCC_MUTAFACTORING, ACCC_MUTASPECIAL, ACCC_MUTARETENTION, ACCC_MUTADISPUTES, ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT, ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE, ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS, ACCC_MUTASTOCK, ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN, ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT, ACCC_JOURNALNO, ACCC_MUTTYPENDX
FROM :1
WHERE ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 AND ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 AND ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' AND ACCC_MUTTYPE < 97
ORDER BY ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO, ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO, ACCC_ACCT_DATE, ACCC_CHANGENO FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

SQL_STMT_U.val:
SELECT
CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASPECIAL) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTARETENTION) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTADISPUTES) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASTOCK) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2))
FROM :1
WHERE ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 AND ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 AND ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' AND (ACCC_MUTTYPE = 97 or ACCC_MUTTYPE = 98)
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS

SELECT
CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAFACTORING) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASPECIAL) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTARETENTION) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTADISPUTES) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASETTLEMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAPAYMENTSETTLE) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAARRANGEMENTS) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTASTOCK) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAEXTRAFIN) AS DECIMAL(13,2)), CAST( SUM(ACCC_MUTAINVESTMENT) AS DECIMAL(13,2))
FROM :1
WHERE ACCC_ACCT_ADMNO = :2 AND ACCC_ACCT_CLNTNO = :3 AND ACCC_ACCT_DATE = ':4' AND ACCC_MUTTYPE = 99
FOR FETCH ONLY OPTIMIZE FOR 100 ROWS
